<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Title</title>
    <style>
        @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Raleway:400,800,900&display=swap');

        * {
            margin: 0;
        }

        .col-12 {
            flex: 0 0 100%;
            max-width: 100%;
        }

        .bg-gray {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.03);
        }

        .h-100 {
            width: auto;
            height: auto;
        }

        .plr-5 {
            padding: 0% 5% 0% 5%;
        }

        .pt-2 {
            padding-top: 2%;
        }

        .pt-3 {
            padding-top: 3%;
        }

        .pt-5 {
            padding-top: 5%;
        }

        .title-text {
            color: rgba(0, 0, 25, 0.70);
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: 1.7em;
        }

        .code-text {
            width: 4.7em;
            padding: .5% .5% 1.5% 2%;
            border-radius: 5px;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.035);
            color: #28C0D1;
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 3.5em;
            letter-spacing: 8px;
        }

        .body-text {
            color: rgba(0, 0, 25, 0.85);
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1.2em;
            letter-spacing: .5px;
        }

        hr {
            margin-top: 10%;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
            border-color: transparent;
        }

        .bg-footer {
            background-color: #28C0D1;
        }

        .footer {
            color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.71);
            font-family: 'Raleway', sans-serif;
            padding: 5% 5% 5% 5%;
            height: 20%;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .plr-5 {
                padding: 3%;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="col-12 bg-gray h-100 plr-5">
    <div class="col-12 pt-2">
        <img class="img-logo" src="https://ik.imagekit.io/pemilo/tr:w-0.3/pemilo_9rk-t7bUx.png"/>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 pt-2">
        <h3 class="title-text">Kode verifikasi kamu:</h3>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 pt-3">
        <h1 class="code-text text-red"><%= code %></h1>
    </div>
    <div class="col-12 pt-5">
        <span class="body-text">Hai, <%= adminsName %>,<br/><br/>Silahkan kembali lagi ke halaman pendaftaran dan masukan kode
            diatas untuk mem-verifikasi email mu!.<br/><br/>Best regards,<br/>Pemilo</span>
    </div>
    <hr/>
    <div class="footer bg-footer">
        <div class="col-12">
            <span class="footer-text">Email ini secara otomatis terkirim dan tidak perlu merespon email ini.<br/>Butuh
                bantuan? <b><a href="#">Hubungi kami</a> </b></span>
        </div>
        <div class="col-12 pt-2">
            <span class="footer-text">Copyrights Â© 2019 <b><a href="#" style="text-decoration: none; color:#146069">Pemilo.id</a></b>. All rights reserved.</span>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>